## **9. Tech Stack Summary (One-Liner)**

> **Frontend:** Next.js + Tailwind CSS + Socket.IO
> **Backend:** FastAPI + WebSockets + SQLAlchemy
> **Database:** PostgreSQL
> **Real-Time:** WebSockets (Socket.IO later)
> **Deployment:** Vercel + AWS / Railway

